               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18391021-name-961" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-961" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-961" type="surname" value="MAINON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-961" type="given" value="LOUIS"></interp>LOUIS MAINON</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Brook-street, Holborn, and am a basket-maker. About seven o'clock at night, on the 16th of October, I saw the prisoner take a basket from inside my shop—he ran away, I pursued, lie dropped it, and the officer stopped him—I lost sight of him as he turned the corners, but when I saw him again, he was running—I am certain of him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18391021-name-962" type="witnessName">
