                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-962" type="given" value="AMBROSE"></interp>AMBROSE MAINON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the prosecutor's son. I heard my father call oat, and saw the prisoner turn into Fox's-court, with a basket in his hand—he dropped it down.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18391021-name-963" type="witnessName">
